    "en": {
      "title": "Father of two killed in fuel queue accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Aluthgama Police say that a person who was queuing on a hire basis to get diesel for an IOC Fuel Hall lorry in Dharga Town has collided with a tipper truck while crossing the main road in front of the petrol station and died, Aluthgama Police said.",
        "The driver who was allegedly involved in the accident had also been returning to Dharga Town from Aluthgama after having dinner at the fuel queue in Dharga Town."
      ],
